                    <div class="t m0 xd h3 y6d ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">XXXXXX</div>
                </div>
                <div class="t m0 x3 h2 y6e ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We shall bill for the payroll management services on monthly basis.</div>
                <div class="t m0 x2 h11 y6f ff2 fs3 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div>
                <div class="t m0 x13 h12 y70 ff1 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0"> <span class="ff2">Payroll Processing Fee is billed monthly based on staff strength:</span></div>
                <div class="t m0 x14 h12 y71 ff1 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0">First 50 employees<span class="_ _5"> </span><span class="ff6">₦</span>XX/Month</div>
                <div class="t m0 x14 h12 y72 ff1 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0">Between 51 – 70 employees<span class="_ _6"> </span><span class="ff6">₦</span>XXX/Month</div>
                <div class="t m0 x14 h12 y73 ff1 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0">Between 71 – 100 employees<span class="_ _7"> </span><span class="ff6">₦</span>XXXX/Month</div>
                <div class="t m0 x14 h12 y74 ff1 fs4 fc3 sc0 ls0 ws0">Between 101 – 150 employees<span class="_ _4"> </span><span class="ff6">₦</span>XXXXX/Month</div>
            </div>
